snippet.title: Rise Online World - Resmi Fragman (Official Trailer) [4K]
snippet.description:
Here is the first look of Rise Online, a MMORPG made in Turkey, by RokoSoft. If you want to find more details about the game, check our website. And do not forget to subscribe for upcoming news and updates.  

You can also discuss about the game in the new forum and social media
